  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"negative x minus w y equals negative 337\"><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>w</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>337</mn></mrow></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"2 x minus w y equals 47\"><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>w</mi><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mn>47</mn></mrow></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In the given system of equations, <math alttext=\"w\"><mi>w</mi>\n</math> is a constant. In the <em>xy</em>-plane, the graphs of these equations intersect at the point <math alttext=\"left parenthesis q comma 19 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mi>q</mi><mo>,</mo><mrow><mn>19</mn></mrow></mrow></mfenced></math>, where <math alttext=\"q\"><mi>q</mi>\n</math> is a constant. What is the value of <math alttext=\"w\"><mi>w</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
